    "MoE split at 16 experts per shard: ~176 MB each (under 250 MB ANE ceiling)",
    "Soft routing: all 32 experts run with sigmoid weights (no topk branching)",
    "Tied embeddings: lm_head weight loaded from embed_tokens.weight slice",
